 *1261126318*Diary of SIGGRAPH Day 3
 The first day's diary was not written because my MacBook would not start, and the second day's diary was not written because I was tired and sleeping.
 Photo taken yesterday:
 <img src="http://gyazo.com/c368c17cb9c4f7166777b4892066b8c0.png">
 
